\pard\sa220\par

\pard\sa180\f0\fs22\b 2. Design Direction\b0\par
\pard\sa120\f0\fs22 The page is now guided by a service-led design principle:\par
\pard\li360\sa100\fs22\bullet\tab Start with current service posture, not static profile data\par
\pard\li360\sa100\fs22\bullet\tab Show only customer context that changes delivery behavior\par
\pard\li360\sa100\fs22\bullet\tab Use CRM as ownership and context, not as the main story\par
\pard\li360\sa100\fs22\bullet\tab Use support and telemetry to explain service risk, not just raw volume\par
\pard\li360\sa220\fs22\bullet\tab End in action, ownership, and next move\par

